182
00:15:38,854 --> 00:15:43,184
- I have your table ready for you.
- Very good, Heinz.

183
00:15:43,317 --> 00:15:47,185
As you know, Comrade Biletnikov
holds a very high rank in the party.

184
00:15:47,321 --> 00:15:49,480
We wish to afford him every courtesy.

185
00:15:49,615 --> 00:15:52,106
But of course, <i>mein General.</i>

186
00:15:52,243 --> 00:15:57,485
Perhaps Comrade Biletnikov could be
persuaded to sing for us this evening.

187
00:15:57,665 --> 00:16:00,416
