- You're an American.
- That's right.

218
00:19:21,241 --> 00:19:24,361
- My uncle was born in America.
- Oh really?

219
00:19:24,495 --> 00:19:27,365
But he was one of the lucky ones.

220
00:19:27,498 --> 00:19:32,539
