We've got the Liberty Bell...

234
00:20:38,652 --> 00:20:41,569
...Disneyland on both coasts.
It's happening.

235
00:20:42,155 --> 00:20:45,606
I'm sorry. I really don't know any German.

236
00:20:45,742 --> 00:20:49,325
